      "summary": "Postdoctoral Researcher working on the High Altitude Water Cherenkov (HAWC) and IceCube Neutrino Observatory experiments. My work focuses on data analysis, simulation, and reconstruction to enhance our understanding of high-energy astrophysical phenomena. I'm the Data Analysis and Software coordinator and lead of the public data release task force for the HAWC Collaboration and I lead the technical and software developement group at HAWC. I work with multi-messenger analysis of neutrino and gamma-ray data in search for unique astrophysical systems and develop Neural Network (NN) based reconstruction algorithms for reconstructing raw data from both observatories for high level data analysis. I also supervise graduate and undergraduate students in the data analysis and machine learning projects.",
